     "titulo": "Pregunta 1 · Dispensadora de libros (lógica)",
     "etiqueta": "SISTEMAS ELÉCTRICOS",
     "menu": "P1 · Dispensadora (lógica)",
     "titulo_corto": "P1",
     "meta": "Pregunta única y obligatoria · 2,5 puntos (a: 1,0 · b: 0,5 · c: 0,5 · d: 0,5)",
     "enunciado_html": "<p>Una máquina dispensadora entrega un libro según las opciones A (novela) y B (ciencia); con ambas pulsadas entrega historia. Además hay dos sensores: C (acceso validado) y D (no hay libros disponibles). El mecanismo abre la compuerta si se cumplen las condiciones de suministro. Se pide:</p><ol type='a'><li>Elaborar la tabla de verdad. <span class='pts'>(1 punto)</span></li><li>Función lógica en primera forma canónica. <span class='pts'>(0,5 puntos)</span></li><li>Simplificar por Karnaugh. <span class='pts'>(0,5 puntos)</span></li><li>Representar el circuito lógico. <span class='pts'>(0,5 puntos)</span></li></ol>",
     "figura_enunciado_svg": "",
     "aplica_html": "<p>La compuerta debe abrirse (S=1) si se solicita algún libro (<b>A o B</b> pulsados), el acceso está validado (<b>C=1</b>) y <b>hay</b> libros disponibles (D=0, es decir \\(\\bar D\\)). Traducimos a lógica, obtenemos la canónica y simplificamos con Karnaugh.</p>",
     "solucion_html": "<h5>a) Tabla de verdad</h5><p>S=1 cuando (A+B)=1, C=1 y D=0; es decir en los minterms 6, 10 y 14:</p><table class='dat'><tr><th>A</th><th>B</th><th>C</th><th>D</th><th>S</th></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style='background:rgba(74,222,128,.14)'><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr></table><h5>b) Primera forma canónica</h5><div class='formula'>$$S=\\bar A B C\\bar D+A\\bar B C\\bar D+ABC\\bar D$$</div><h5>c) Simplificación por Karnaugh</h5><figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 470 320' width='100%' style='max-width:430px;height:auto' fill='none' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif'><text x='110' y='58' fill='#94a3b8' font-size='12'>AB\\CD</text><text x='179' y='58' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>00</text><text x='237' y='58' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>01</text><text x='295' y='58' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>11</text><text x='353' y='58' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>10</text><text x='128' y='99' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>00</text><rect x='150' y='72' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='179' y='100' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='208' y='72' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='237' y='100' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='266' y='72' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='295' y='100' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='324' y='72' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='353' y='100' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><text x='128' y='143' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>01</text><rect x='150' y='116' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='179' y='144' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='208' y='116' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='237' y='144' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='266' y='116' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='295' y='144' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='324' y='116' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='353' y='144' fill='#4ade80' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><text x='128' y='187' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>11</text><rect x='150' y='160' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='179' y='188' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='208' y='160' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='237' y='188' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='266' y='160' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='295' y='188' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='324' y='160' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='353' y='188' fill='#4ade80' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><text x='128' y='231' fill='#7dd3fc' font-size='13' text-anchor='middle'>10</text><rect x='150' y='204' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='179' y='232' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='208' y='204' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='237' y='232' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='266' y='204' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='295' y='232' fill='#64748b' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>0</text><rect x='324' y='204' width='58' height='44' fill='none' stroke='#334155' stroke-width='1.3'/><text x='353' y='232' fill='#4ade80' font-size='17' font-weight='700' text-anchor='middle'>1</text><rect x='319' y='112' width='68' height='96' rx='9' fill='none' stroke='#a78bfa' stroke-width='2.2'/><text x='384' y='143' fill='#c4b5fd' font-size='12'>B·C·D&#773;</text><rect x='315' y='152' width='76' height='104' rx='12' fill='none' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='2.2' stroke-dasharray='5 3'/><text x='384' y='231' fill='#fbbf24' font-size='12'>A·C·D&#773;</text></svg><figcaption>Grupos B&#183;C&#183;D&#773; (violeta) y A&#183;C&#183;D&#773; (naranja).</figcaption></figure><div class='formula'>$$S=BC\\bar D+AC\\bar D=(A+B)\\,C\\,\\bar D$$</div><div class='res'><b>S = (A + B) · C · D&#773;</b></div><h5>d) Circuito lógico</h5><figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 500 260' width='100%' style='max-width:470px;height:auto' fill='none' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif' stroke='#e2e8f0' stroke-width='1.8'><text x='16' y='55' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='14'>A</text><text x='16' y='95' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='14'>B</text><text x='16' y='150' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='14'>C</text><text x='16' y='215' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='14'>D</text><line x1='30' y1='50' x2='120' y2='50'/><line x1='30' y1='90' x2='120' y2='90'/><path d='M112 34 Q150 34 190 70 Q150 106 112 106 Q132 70 112 34 Z' fill='none' stroke='#34d399' stroke-width='2.2'/><line x1='190' y1='70' x2='300' y2='70'/><line x1='300' y1='70' x2='300' y2='96'/><line x1='30' y1='210' x2='90' y2='210'/><polygon points='90,196 90,224 118,210' fill='none' stroke='#a78bfa' stroke-width='2'/><circle cx='123' cy='210' r='4' fill='none' stroke='#a78bfa' stroke-width='2'/><text x='130' y='202' fill='#c4b5fd' font-size='12'>D&#773;</text><line x1='30' y1='150' x2='300' y2='150'/><line x1='128' y1='210' x2='300' y2='210'/><line x1='300' y1='210' x2='300' y2='204'/><path d='M300 60 L340 60 A50 50 0 0 1 340 200 L300 200 Z' fill='none' stroke='#38bdf8' stroke-width='2.4'/><line x1='300' y1='96' x2='300' y2='96'/><line x1='390' y1='130' x2='460' y2='130'/><text x='466' y='135' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15'>S</text></svg><figcaption>Una OR (A+B), un inversor para D&#773; y una AND de tres entradas.</figcaption></figure>"
