     "enunciado_html": "<p>Dado el diagrama de bloques de la figura, obtén la función de transferencia. <span class='pts'>(2,5 puntos)</span></p>",
     "figura_enunciado_svg": "<figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 900 380' width='100%' style='max-width:820px;height:auto' fill='none' stroke='#cbd5e1' stroke-width='2' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif' font-size='14'><defs><marker id='ar' markerWidth='9' markerHeight='8' refX='7' refY='3' orient='auto'><path d='M0,0 L7,3 L0,6 Z' fill='#cbd5e1'/></marker></defs><line x1='66' y1='175' x2='118' y2='175' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='134' cy='175' r='15' stroke='#e2e8f0'/><line x1='124' y1='164' x2='144' y2='186' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='144' y1='164' x2='124' y2='186' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='150' y1='175' x2='190' y2='175' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='190' y='153' width='78' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='229.0' y='180.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P1</text><line x1='268' y1='175' x2='350' y2='175' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='350' y='153' width='78' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='389.0' y='180.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P2</text><line x1='428' y1='175' x2='486' y2='175' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='502' cy='175' r='15' stroke='#e2e8f0'/><line x1='492' y1='164' x2='512' y2='186' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='512' y1='164' x2='492' y2='186' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='518' y1='175' x2='560' y2='175' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='560' y='153' width='78' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='599.0' y='180.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P5</text><line x1='638' y1='175' x2='800' y2='175' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><text x='40' y='180' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>X</text><text x='812' y='180' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>Z</text><circle cx='300' cy='175' r='3.2' fill='#cbd5e1' stroke='none'/><circle cx='680' cy='175' r='3.2' fill='#cbd5e1' stroke='none'/><text x='116' y='161' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='120' y='201' fill='#fb7185' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>−</text><text x='486' y='161' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='490' y='201' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><line x1='300' y1='175' x2='300' y2='95' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='300' y1='95' x2='502' y2='95' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='502' y1='95' x2='502' y2='157' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='430' y='300' width='78' height='40' rx='5' stroke='#a78bfa'/><text x='469.0' y='325.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P4</text><rect x='250' y='300' width='78' height='40' rx='5' stroke='#a78bfa'/><text x='289.0' y='325.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P3</text><line x1='680' y1='175' x2='680' y2='320' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='680' y1='320' x2='508' y2='320' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><line x1='430' y1='320' x2='328' y2='320' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><line x1='250' y1='320' x2='134' y2='320' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='134' y1='320' x2='134' y2='193' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/></svg><figcaption>Camino directo con una rama que puentea P<sub>2</sub> (paralelo 1 + P<sub>2</sub>) y realimentación P<sub>3</sub>·P<sub>4</sub> negativa.</figcaption></figure>",
     "aplica_html": "<p>La señal tras P<sub>1</sub> llega a la salida por dos caminos que se suman: uno directo y otro a través de P<sub>2</sub> (equivalen a \\(1+P_2\\)). El lazo se cierra negativamente por P<sub>3</sub>·P<sub>4</sub>.</p>",
     "solucion_html": "<h5>Rama en paralelo (bypass de P<sub>2</sub>)</h5><p>La señal a la salida de P<sub>1</sub> se suma consigo misma a través de P<sub>2</sub>: equivale a \\((1+P_2)\\). El camino directo es \\(P_1(1+P_2)P_5\\).</p><h5>Lazo de realimentación</h5><p>Realimentación negativa \\(P_3P_4\\) sobre todo el camino directo:</p><div class='formula'>$$\\boxed{\\dfrac{Z}{X}=\\dfrac{P_1P_5(1+P_2)}{1+P_1P_3P_4P_5(1+P_2)}}$$</div><div class='res'><b>Z/X = P<sub>1</sub>P<sub>5</sub>(1 + P<sub>2</sub>) / [1 + P<sub>1</sub>P<sub>3</sub>P<sub>4</sub>P<sub>5</sub>(1 + P<sub>2</sub>)]</b></div>"
    },
    {
     "id": "q4b",
     "titulo": "Pregunta 4.2 (Opción B) · Reducción de un sistema de control",
     "etiqueta": "OPCIÓN B",
     "menu": "P4.2 (B) · Sistema de control",
     "titulo_corto": "P4.2",
     "meta": "2,5 puntos",
     "enunciado_html": "<p>Simplifica el siguiente sistema de control hasta conseguir la función de transferencia. <span class='pts'>(2,5 puntos)</span></p>",
     "figura_enunciado_svg": "<figure class='fig'><svg viewBox='0 0 900 420' width='100%' style='max-width:820px;height:auto' fill='none' stroke='#cbd5e1' stroke-width='2' font-family='Inter,system-ui,sans-serif' font-size='14'><defs><marker id='ar' markerWidth='9' markerHeight='8' refX='7' refY='3' orient='auto'><path d='M0,0 L7,3 L0,6 Z' fill='#cbd5e1'/></marker></defs><line x1='66' y1='175' x2='118' y2='175' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='134' cy='175' r='15' stroke='#e2e8f0'/><line x1='124' y1='164' x2='144' y2='186' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='144' y1='164' x2='124' y2='186' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='150' y1='175' x2='190' y2='175' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><circle cx='190' cy='175' r='3.2' fill='#cbd5e1' stroke='none'/><rect x='240' y='90' width='80' height='42' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='280.0' y='116.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P1</text><line x1='190' y1='175' x2='190' y2='111' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='190' y1='111' x2='240' y2='111' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><line x1='320' y1='111' x2='545' y2='111' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='545' y1='111' x2='561' y2='157' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><rect x='240' y='240' width='80' height='42' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='280.0' y='266.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P2</text><rect x='370' y='240' width='80' height='42' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='410.0' y='266.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P3</text><line x1='190' y1='175' x2='190' y2='261' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='190' y1='261' x2='240' y2='261' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><line x1='320' y1='261' x2='370' y2='261' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><line x1='450' y1='261' x2='545' y2='261' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='545' y1='261' x2='561' y2='193' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='577' cy='175' r='15' stroke='#e2e8f0'/><line x1='566' y1='164' x2='588' y2='186' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='588' y1='164' x2='566' y2='186' stroke='#94a3b8'/><line x1='593' y1='175' x2='660' y2='175' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><circle cx='628' cy='175' r='3.2' fill='#cbd5e1' stroke='none'/><rect x='660' y='153' width='80' height='44' rx='5' stroke='#22d3ee'/><text x='700.0' y='180.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P4</text><line x1='740' y1='175' x2='800' y2='175' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><text x='40' y='180' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>X</text><text x='812' y='180' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>Z</text><text x='116' y='161' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='120' y='201' fill='#fb7185' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>−</text><text x='561' y='161' fill='#4ade80' font-size='14' text-anchor='start'>+</text><text x='565' y='201' fill='#fb7185' font-size='16' text-anchor='start'>−</text><rect x='370' y='350' width='80' height='42' rx='5' stroke='#a78bfa'/><text x='410.0' y='376.0' fill='#e2e8f0' font-size='15' text-anchor='middle'>P5</text><line x1='628' y1='175' x2='628' y2='371' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='628' y1='371' x2='450' y2='371' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/><line x1='370' y1='371' x2='134' y2='371' stroke='#cbd5e1'/><line x1='134' y1='371' x2='134' y2='193' stroke='#cbd5e1' marker-end='url(#ar)'/></svg><figcaption>Dos ramas en paralelo (P<sub>1</sub> y P<sub>2</sub>·P<sub>3</sub>) que se restan, seguidas de P<sub>4</sub>, con realimentación P<sub>5</sub> negativa.</figcaption></figure>",
     "aplica_html": "<p>Las ramas P<sub>1</sub> y P<sub>2</sub>P<sub>3</sub> parten del mismo punto y se combinan en el comparador (una con signo +, otra con &minus;): equivalen a \\((P_1-P_2P_3)\\). Después va P<sub>4</sub> y el lazo se cierra con P<sub>5</sub> negativo.</p>",
     "solucion_html": "<h5>Ramas en paralelo</h5><p>La señal tras el primer comparador se bifurca por P<sub>1</sub> (+) y por P<sub>2</sub>P<sub>3</sub> (&minus;): equivale a \\((P_1-P_2P_3)\\).</p><h5>Lazo con P<sub>5</sub> (negativo) y P<sub>4</sub> a la salida</h5><div class='formula'>$$N=\\frac{P_1-P_2P_3}{1+P_5(P_1-P_2P_3)}\\,X\\qquad Z=P_4\\,N$$</div><div class='formula'>$$\\boxed{\\dfrac{Z}{X}=\\dfrac{P_4\\,(P_1-P_2P_3)}{1+P_5(P_1-P_2P_3)}}$$</div><div class='res'><b>Z/X = P<sub>4</sub>(P<sub>1</sub> − P<sub>2</sub>P<sub>3</sub>) / [1 + P<sub>5</sub>(P<sub>1</sub> − P<sub>2</sub>P<sub>3</sub>)]</b></div>"
    }
